sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Client as Client
    participant Facade as Facade<br/>(searchHotels)
    participant Adapter as BookingComAdapter
    participant CB as CircuitBreaker
    participant API as Mock Hotel API<br/>(Booking.com)

    Client->>Facade: GET /hotels?city=rome
    Facade->>Adapter: searchHotels("rome")
    Adapter->>CB: allowRequest()
    CB-->>Adapter: true (CLOSED)

    rect rgb(230, 245, 230)
    Note over Adapter,API: Poging 1 — succespad
    Adapter->>API: GET /hotels?city=rome
    API-->>Adapter: 200 OK (ruwe Booking-JSON)
    Adapter->>CB: recordSuccess()
    Adapter->>Adapter: _translate(raw) → HotelResult[]
    Adapter-->>Facade: HotelResult[]
    Facade-->>Client: 200 OK (interne modellen + circuit-status)
    end

    Note over Client,API: ───── Faalscenario (FAILURE_MODE = "flaky" / "timeout" / "error") ─────

    Client->>Facade: GET /hotels?city=rome
    Facade->>Adapter: searchHotels("rome")
    Adapter->>CB: allowRequest()
    CB-->>Adapter: true

    rect rgb(252, 232, 232)
    Note over Adapter,API: Retry-lus met exponentiële backoff
    Adapter->>API: Poging 1
    API--xAdapter: timeout / 500
    Adapter->>CB: recordFailure() (1/3)
    Note right of Adapter: wacht 1s

    Adapter->>API: Poging 2
    API--xAdapter: timeout / 500
    Adapter->>CB: recordFailure() (2/3)
    Note right of Adapter: wacht 2s

    Adapter->>API: Poging 3
    API--xAdapter: timeout / 500
    Adapter->>CB: recordFailure() (3/3) → OPEN
    end

    Adapter-->>Facade: Error: "All 3 attempts failed"
    Facade-->>Client: 503 Service Unavailable<br/>(circuit: OPEN)

    Note over Client,API: ───── Volgende request terwijl circuit OPEN is ─────

    Client->>Facade: GET /hotels?city=rome
    Facade->>Adapter: searchHotels("rome")
    Adapter->>CB: allowRequest()
    CB-->>Adapter: false (OPEN — fail fast)
    Adapter-->>Facade: Error: "Circuit breaker is OPEN"
    Facade-->>Client: 503 (geen HTTP-call naar provider)
